A video that has gone viral shows a womam in a physical altercation with her manager inside the supermarket where she works. The person who posted the video identified the supermarket as a Spar in Nelspruit,Mpumalanga. In the 16 second clip,a security guard is seen restraining the woman from the man,and as the guard pulls her away she yells ,"ngiyekele uyangi jwayela lomlungu"(let go of me this white man is disrespecting me). The man is seen trying to fix his shirt afterwards.   According to TimesLive,the man is the store manager and the woman, an employee, have opened cases of assault against each other. The site quotes Mpumalanga police spokesperson Brig Leonard Hlathi  who confirmed  that the incident had taken place at a Spar store on Tuesday. “Police are investigating two cases of assault common [cross charges] in relation to an incident which took place on February 18 2020 about 3pm in one of the shops at Courtside Shopping Complex,” he said. “According to information at police disposal an argument between a manager and an employee started and it led to a physical altercation. The manager and the employee laid charges of assault common against each other at Nelspruit SAPS.” No arrests have been made. 